      "content": "it's not just random though... it's like it's actually trying to ruin my stuff. it posted some really controversial things about my job yesterday. i'm literally terrified to even log in now. if an ai is actually running my accounts, how would i even tell? like, how do i know if the 'me' online isn't just the ai version anymore?",
